い情報が寄せられる。その中で、明らかに関連がなさそうな別の事件の情報が気になった安堂（松山ケンイチ）は、小野崎（鳴海唯）と共に被害者の父・羽鳥（田辺誠一）を訪ねる。しかし調査を進める最中、予期せぬ連絡が入り・・・\",\"url\":\"https://www.web.nhk/tv/an/drama-themis/pl/series-tep-32VWPKM6NX/ep/E6JLGKRYQZ\",\"identifierGroup\":{\"environmentId\":\"hskOriginal\",\"broadcastEventId\":\"g1-130-2026030308105\",\"serviceId\":\"g1\",\"streamType\":\"vod\"},\"detailedContentStatus\":{\"environmentId\":\"hskOriginal\",\"streamType\":\"vod\",\"contentStatus\":\"ready\"},\"detailedVideoDescriptor\":\"https://archive.hsk.st.nhk/npd3/7fe0-0400/20260303/1fa9-1-3-a52dfb0e492b455783c10ab473e1148b/videoinfo-4aedbfe4e112c0c0ec3458fad795a1e7.json\",\"expires\":\"2026-03-10T22:44:30+09:00\",\"duration\":\"PT44M29S\",\"startDate\":\"2026-03-03T22:00:00+09:00\",\"endDate\":\"2026-03-03T22:44:30+09:00\",\"isDivided\":false,\"publication\":[{\"id\":\"g1-130-2026030308105\",\"url\":\"https://api-local.ss.org.nhk/r8/t/broadcastevent/be/g1-130-2026030308105.json\",\"isLiveBroadcast\":true}],\"hasPart\":[],\"uploadDate\":\"2026-03-03T22:44:30+09:00\"}],\"citation\":[],\"detailedPinnedCitation\":[],\"sameAs\":[],\"correction\":[],\"url\":\"https://api-local.ss.org.nhk/r8/t/tvepisode/te/E6JLGKRYQZ.json\",\"canonical\":\"https://www.web.nhk/tv/an/drama-themis/pl/series-tep-32VWPKM6NX/ep/E6JLGKRYQZ\",\"associatedMedia\":[{\"id\":\"bcUploadTrailer1\",\"name\":\"テミスの不確かな法廷\",\"description\":\"(7)裁判所主導の職権主義\\n\",\"embedUrl\":\"https://www.nhk.jp/assets/players/bc/v3/index.html?account=6415847969001\u0026player=YVUjvvMQb\u0026videoId=6389855566112\",\"identifierGroup\":{\"environmentId\":\"bcUploadTrailer\",\"streamType\":\"clip\",\"bcAccountId\":\"6415847969001\",\"bcVideoId\":\"6389855566112\"},\"detailedContentStatus\":{\"environmentId\":\"bcUploadTrailer\",\"streamType\":\"clip\",\"contentStatus\":\"ready\"},\"thumbnail\":{\"main\":{\"url\":\"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvepisode/te/E6JLGKRYQZ/E6JLGKRYQZ-eyecatch_60932cb384149c5899da1bae99a6a537.png\",\"width\":1920,\"height\":1080},\"mediu