郎と夫婦になる許しを得るため中村に戻る。意外にも父・喜左衛門（大倉孝二）から手厚く迎えられるが・・・\",\"dateCreated\":\"2026-01-13T18:33:17+09:00\",\"dateModified\":\"2026-03-02T16:30:36+09:00\",\"actor\":[{\"person\":{\"identifierGroup\":{\"npgId\":\"29D4D7A7-E3F2-4E1F-94CA-046080070DC0\",\"wikidataId\":\"Q11444506\"},\"roleName\":\"Actor\",\"displayRoleName\":\"俳優\",\"name\":\"仲野 太賀\",\"detailedNameRuby\":\"なかの たいが\",\"familyName\":\"仲野\",\"givenName\":\"太賀\",\"detailedFamilyNameRuby\":\"なかの\",\"detailedGivenNameRuby\":\"たいが\",\"detailedNameDescription\":\"\",\"honorificSuffix\":\"\",\"jobTitle\":[],\"memberOf\":[],\"image\":{\"main\":{\"url\":\"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_2e4f43bc990dfaa6d4477eded7ef370a.png\",\"width\":1080,\"height\":1080},\"medium\":{\"url\":\"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_23f990abd5ef3e1f02468ff2e9fe7fc5.png\",\"width\":640,\"height\":640},\"small\":{\"url\":\"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_0a9515dff6449441235f861779b8ea9b.png\",\"width\":200,\"height\":200}},\"characterName\":\"小一郎（豊臣秀長）\",\"detailedCharacterNameRuby\":\"こいちろう（とよとみ ひでなが）\",\"description\":\"天下人・豊臣秀吉の弟\\n登場時の名は小一郎。兄の天下取りをいちずに支え続けた「天下一の補佐役」といわれている。\",\"detailedWork\":[],\"hasOccupation\":[]}},{\"person\":{\"identifierGroup\":{\"npgId\":\"D690F0C8-05B8-4A71-9A1E-13B8A756E70D\",\"wikidataId\":\"Q1058963\"},\"roleName\":\"Actor\",\"displayRoleName\":\"俳優\",\"name\":\"池松 壮亮\",\"detailedNameRuby\":\"いけまつ そうすけ\",\"familyName\":\"池松\",\"givenName\":\"壮亮\",\"detailedFamilyNameRuby\":\"いけまつ\",\"detailedGivenNameRuby\":\"そうすけ\",\"detailedNameDescription\":\"\",\"honorificSuffix\":\"\",\"jobTitle\":[],\"memberOf\":[],\"image\":{\"main\":{\"url\":\"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_4f93e5276609f6f43e9c328f965eb6e6.png\",\"width\":1080,\"height\":1080},\"medium\":{\"url\":\"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_3d74da780b5e535b14406469f0191f93.png\",\"width\":640,\"height\":640},\"small\":{\"url\":\"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_64c55d28509ee3a35e5bb0f5858e4fbe.png\",\"width\":200,\"height\":200}},\"characterName\":\"藤吉郎（豊臣秀吉）\",\"detailedCharacterNameRuby\":\"とうきちろう（とよとみ ひでよし）\",\"description\":\"小一郎を乱世に巻き込んだ野心家の兄\\n小一郎の３歳年上の兄。登場時の名は藤吉郎。尾張中村の貧しい農家で生まれ育ったが、主君である戦国武将・織田信長のもとでメキメキと頭角をあらわし、ついには天下統一を果たす。\",\"detailedWork\":[],\"hasOccupation\":[]}},{\"person\":{\"identifierGroup\":{\"npgId\":\"04E1F915-FCA1-441E-B5E2-5D60F7FE75D6\",\"wikidataId\":\"Q11284289\"},\"roleName\":\"Actor\",\"displayRoleName\":\"俳優\",\"name\":\"浜辺 美波\",\"detailedNameRuby\":\"はまべ みなみ\",\"familyName\":\"浜辺\",\"givenName\":\"美波\",\"detailedFamilyNameRuby\":\"はまべ\",\"detailedGivenNameRuby\":\"みなみ\",\"detailedNameDescription\":\"\",\"honorificSuffix\":\"\",\"jobTitle\":[],\"memberOf\":[],\"image\":{\"main\":{\"url\":\"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_ef58d771f0c2463b1124572a35f45a72.png\",\"width\":1080,\"height\":1080},\"medium\":{\"url\":\"https://img.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_d07a6eeeaa595b2204403054dc3aaab8.png\",\"width\":640,\"height\":640},\"small\":{\"url\":\"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/P52L88MYXY/P52L88MYXY-person_1cf30951d5408cccb8dc6d45652cd9d4.png\",\"width\":200,\"height\":200}},\"characterName\":\"寧々\",\"detailedCharacterNameRuby\":\"ねね\",\"description\":\"夫の秀吉とともに天下人への階段を昇りつめる\\n豊臣秀吉の正妻。秀吉が関白に就任したのちは北政所（きたのまんどころ）と称される。\\n負けず嫌いの性格で、夫の秀吉とともに出世街道を駆け抜ける。\\nやがて庶民の娘から“戦国のファーストレディ”へと昇りつめる。\",\"detailedWork\":[],\"hasOccupation\":[]}},{\"person\":{\"identifierGroup\":{\"npgId\":\"00110902-AE66-45F8-B48D-E45DBA3F0CA8\",\"wikidataId\":\"Q48758750\"},\"roleName\":\"Actor\",\"displayRoleName\":\"俳優\",\"name\":\"白石 聖\",\"detailedNameRuby\":\"しらいし せい\",\"familyName\":\"白石\",\"givenName\":\"聖\",\"detailedFamilyNameRu