640,\"height\":360}},{\"large\":{\"url\":\"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvepisode/te/N3922VZ63P/N3922VZ63P-eyecatches_0eabd5fbea98db9c05eeb90881366067.jpg\",\"width\":3840,\"height\":2160},\"main\":{\"url\":\"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvepisode/te/N3922VZ63P/N3922VZ63P-eyecatches_e70a4a26373af7dc7d2706288a7dffe5.jpg\",\"width\":1920,\"height\":1080},\"medium\":{\"url\":\"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvepisode/te/N3922VZ63P/N3922VZ63P-eyecatches_d8d576976ec48a27813cee9e9a363b60.jpg\",\"width\":1280,\"height\":720},\"small\":{\"url\":\"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvepisode/te/N3922VZ63P/N3922VZ63P-eyecatches_899cdff38c9a8211847251ff6fc0a27b.jpg\",\"width\":640,\"height\":360}},{\"large\":{\"url\":\"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvepisode/te/N3922VZ63P/N3922VZ63P-eyecatches_6728c898ffd9afff9acea5b2013d53c1.jpg\",\"width\":3840,\"height\":2160},\"main\":{\"url\":\"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvepisode/te/N3922VZ63P/N3922VZ63P-eyecatches_2ec7ad3875ed43958077d25d6596c6c5.jpg\",\"width\":1920,\"height\":1080},\"medium\":{\"url\":\"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvepisode/te/N3922VZ63P/N3922VZ63P-eyecatches_57ebef3346e273094030d8a2bc8d1234.jpg\",\"width\":1280,\"height\":720},\"small\":{\"url\":\"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvepisode/te/N3922VZ63P/N3922VZ63P-eyecatches_664e5f109c6564e80616aff2563e02aa.jpg\",\"width\":640,\"height\":360}}],\"video\":[{\"id\":\"hskOriginal-g1-130-2026030107100\",\"name\":\"豊臣兄弟！（８）墨俣（すのまた）一夜城\",\"description\":\"小一郎（仲野太賀）らは墨俣へ出陣。だが信長（小栗旬）の真の狙いは墨俣ではなく、美濃三人衆の一人・安藤守就（田中哲司）が守る北方城だった。藤吉郎（池松壮亮）は、美濃国主・斎藤龍興（濱田龍臣）の目を北方城から逸らすための捨て石と承知の上で、墨俣に砦を築く大作戦に着手する。一方、直（白石聖）は、小一郎と夫婦になる許しを得るため中村に戻る。意外にも父・喜左衛門（大倉孝二）から手厚く迎えられるが・・・\",\"url\":\"https://www.web.nhk/tv/an/toyotomi-kyodai/pl/series-tep-P52L88MYXY/ep/N3922VZ63P\",\"identifierGroup\":{\"environmentId\":\"hskOriginal\",\"broadcastEventId\":\"g1-130-2026030107100\",\"serviceId\":\"g1\",\"streamType\":\"v