ロッソは謎の人物と連絡をとりあっているようだが…。\\n\\n原題：The Thundermans : Undercover\\n制作：2025年 アメリカ\\n\",\"detailedCatch\":\"帰ってきた「サンダーマン」 フィービー、マックス、クロエが素性を隠して秘密の捜査！[全13回]\",\"logo\":{\"main\":{\"url\":\"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/J5N1R29NKP/J5N1R29NKP-logo_74ef06fd440caaa9d97aff4c5c2ab3df.jpg\",\"width\":1080,\"height\":1080},\"medium\":{\"url\":\"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/J5N1R29NKP/J5N1R29NKP-logo_fdc105e2b68bcecc5d39610a9382e988.jpg\",\"width\":640,\"height\":640},\"small\":{\"url\":\"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/J5N1R29NKP/J5N1R29NKP-logo_6c1e491f9fc15c1c386355d4d873b3bf.jpg\",\"width\":200,\"height\":200}},\"eyecatch\":{\"large\":{\"url\":\"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/J5N1R29NKP/J5N1R29NKP-eyecatch_2a3aff5a26f88a0aeafc1d758b24dfa2.jpg\",\"width\":3840,\"height\":2160},\"main\":{\"url\":\"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/J5N1R29NKP/J5N1R29NKP-eyecatch_89a09384518ac9ecb0401835548ddef4.jpg\",\"width\":1920,\"height\":1080},\"medium\":{\"url\":\"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/J5N1R29NKP/J5N1R29NKP-eyecatch_4dd6526e212839c55f632034bfa30710.jpg\",\"width\":1280,\"height\":720},\"small\":{\"url\":\"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/J5N1R29NKP/J5N1R29NKP-eyecatch_7c51081d1ae4c70360cc8281b602ddf3.jpg\",\"width\":640,\"height\":360}},\"hero\":{\"main\":{\"url\":\"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/J5N1R29NKP/J5N1R29NKP-hero_6deb1b6d80946924f01be4c469081808.jpg\",\"width\":1920,\"height\":640},\"medium\":{\"url\":\"https://imgu.web.nhk/static/assets/images/tvseries/ts/J5N1R29NKP/J5N1R29NKP-hero_34fef2285dc63b8abeb2e4185ae1a92a.jpg\",\"width\":1080,\"height\":360}},\"style\":{\"textLight\":\"#000000\",\"textDark\":\"#FFFFFF\",\"linkLight\":\"#E72400\",\"linkDark\":\"#FF4928\",\"primaryLight\":\"#FF2800\",\"primaryDark\":\"#FF2800\"},\"additionalProperty\":{\"publishLevel\":\"full\",\"layoutPattern\":\"summ